1
00:00:00,400 --> 00:00:04,270
Siddhartha Gautama,
the Buddha,

2
00:00:04,510 --> 00:00:07,840
drew a circle with
a piece of red chalk

3
00:00:08,080 --> 00:00:10,240
and said:

4
00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:12,880
"When men,
even unknowingly,

5
00:00:13,120 --> 00:00:15,280
are to meet one day,

6
00:00:15,520 --> 00:00:17,650
whatever may
befall each,

7
00:00:17,890 --> 00:00:20,550
whatever their
diverging paths,

8
00:00:20,790 --> 00:00:22,450
on the said day,

9
00:00:22,730 --> 00:00:25,020
they will inevitably
come together

10
00:00:25,460 --> 00:00:27,620
in the red circle."

11
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:35,074
